title.narrative: STRATEGIC INFORMATION, RESEARCH AND KNOWLEDGE MANAGEMENT

description.narrative: More high-quality research and derivative knowledge products, with specific focus on the most disadvantaged children in MENA, are available and used., which contributes to Cross-Sectoral Communication For Development, Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Evaluation And Research, Skills Development, Water. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: UNICEF demonstrates enhanced evidence-informed leadership and broadened partnerships to promote child rights and wellbeing across MENA.
